        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Hd1e108">Rubrica 38</head>
        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De futuro fine mundi: et futura resurrectione mortuorum: et
          futuro vniuersali iudicio dei secundum christianam religionem
        </head>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-d1e114">
           De futuro fine mundi et 
           <lb ed="#O"/>futura resurrectione mortuorum 
           <lb ed="#O"/>et futuro uniuersali iudicio dei 
           <lb ed="#O"/>secundum christianam religionem. Rubrica 38
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-d1e123">
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Rd1e120">PSalmista. 101. psalmus</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Qd1e127">Celi pe<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ribunt.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-d1e133">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Rd1e132">SAlamon <!--line bumps up--> im prouer. capitulo 11.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Qd1e137">Non <!--line bumps back down--> proderunt diuitie in 
           <lb ed="#O"/>in die ultionis iustitia autem 
           liberabit a morte.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-d1e146">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Rd1e147">MAlachias pro<!--line bumps up-->pheta. capitulo 4.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Qd1e150">dies <!--line bumps back down--> ueniet succen<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>sus 
           quisi caminus et erunt superbi 
           <lb ed="#O"/>et omnes facientes impietatem stipula et 
           <lb ed="#O"/>inflammabit eos dies ueniens</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-d1e158">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Rd1e161">MAttheus in euan. capitulo 12.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Qd1e162">.<!--line bumps up--> Omne <!--line bumps back down--> uer<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>bum 
           <lb ed="#O"/>ociosum quod locuti fuerint homines 
           <lb ed="#O"/>reddent rationem de eo in die iudicii ex 
           <lb ed="#O"/>uerbis enim tuis iustificaberis. et ex uer<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>bis 
           tuis condennaberis.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-d1e172">
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Rd1e175">capitulo 13.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Qd1e174">In 
           <lb ed="#O"/>consummatio saeculi. mittet filius hominis 
           <lb ed="#O"/>angelos suos et colligent de regno 
           <lb ed="#O"/>suo omnia scandala et omnes qui fa<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ciunt 
           iniquitatem et mittent eos in car<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>mibus
           ignis. ibi erit fletus et stri<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>dor 
           dentium. Tunc iusti fulgebunt 
           <lb ed="#O"/>sic sol in regno patris eorum.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-d1e193">
           ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d10089-Qd1e195">In 
           <lb ed="#O"/>consummatione seculi exibunt angeli 
           <lb ed="#O"/>et separabunt malos de medio iustorum 
           <lb ed="#O"/>et mittent eos in caminum ignis ar<lb ed="#O" break="no"/><!--[rest of word missing]-->
           <pb ed="#O" n="29-r"/>
           <cb ed="#O" n="a"/>
